description._content: Location: Cambodia Date: 14 March 1955 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Scene from one of the Cambodian dances performed on the occasion of the King's banquet to the officers of H.M.S. 'Opossum' The King's granddaughter is in the centre. Location: Cambodia Date: 14 March 1955 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Reading from left to right: H.H. Consul; His Excellency Leng Ngeth, Prime Minister; H.M. Ambassador; H.M. Norodom Suramarit; Commander S.A. Porter, D.S.C. , R.N; His Excellency Khim Tit; H.M. Naval Attaché. Location: Cambodia Date: 14 March 1955 ------------------------------------------------------ Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/420.
